comments.body: If there is not fix posible at the moment, there is a way to select previous version of hyperloop? I canÂ´t compile, Tested also in manjaro linux.

UPDATE
I deleted the /build/ folder, now the compiler skipes the hyperloop assembly, proyect compiles but it does not import hyperloop in app

I removed everything, uninstalled all, reinstalled again but used sdk 6.1.2 hyperloop 2.2.1 and it works again..

P.D. when I create a new proyect to enable hyperloop it got installed wrong, instead of add the hyperloop folder in modules and plugin folder, it creates a hyperloop-2.2.1 folder in root of .titanium folder. So I moved manually folders accordingly.

This ticket can be closed as I fixed by reinstalling and cleaning build folder
